S.FORM: kasulin micaliw tu lebung adada' ku tangila sapuelac ngatu cacay anu mikacaw kami tu kasulin , kya kasulin macaliw tu lebung saca buhang sa, caay haw kisu adada' ku tangila ? kanahantu matengil tu ku suni',caay tu kapah ku suni', caay kasiwatan ku suni' haw? kya mahiza saw? uyniyan sa, u tangila nu mita, ilabu' a tangila, sipiatep nay bali kya. izaw ku duhpicay a telis , kya ngangan nu hulam sa, u "kumuo鼓膜". ilabu' nu kumuo maziket tulu a wukak, taneng patudu' ninel nu kumuo, tina kakitizaan singangan ku "teban-tangila ". i demiad sa, u bali-sapiatep nu teban-tangila mahiza nu hekalay, taneng sapalalen . nika anu ihekalay a bali-sapiatep tasul talakaw saca puenel sa, uyniyan a sapiatep caay tu sapalalen, bucici tu ku talakaway a bali-sapiatep tayza puenelay-sapiatep. ku kumuo talabu' saca tahekal, caay tu kakapah ku tangila nu mita. ngatuc tusa micumud tu lebung ku kasulin, kya bali-sapiatep tansul amatasasa', talakaw tu ku bali-sapiatep ilabu' nu teban-tangila, uzama sa, bucici tu ku kumuo nay labu' tahekal. sisa, adada' tu ku tangila nu mita. mahiza tu mikacaw tu hikuki, tapabaw ku hikuki, adada' tu ku tangila nu mita. usakasa, mapuenel ku bali-sapiatep ihekal nu hikuki. u belih sa, anu mikacaw kami tu tianti , tansul sa tasasa' kya tianti, tansul talakaw ku bali-sapiatep nu tianti. bucici kumuo nay hekal talabu', mahiza sa, adada' tu ku tangila nu mita. musepi , sihusu matulin teban-tangil atu cihe-salaedan(鼻腔,salaedan空間), u tangila-takulaw-husu . pisuwab saca pienuc taneng mibuhat tu tangila-takulaw-husu, miedap sapalaen bali-sapiatep nu teban-tangil aut hekal-tangila . anu mahiza sa, caay tu kaadada' ku tangila. namakayniyan a nasulitan nasakamuwan atu natinengan Wikipayke paybalucu'ay pulungamin a cudad-耳 Protein behind hearing 3D Ear page Details of various ear problems Ear wiggling mechanism unmasked Cotton swabs can pose serious health risk: coroner from ctv.ca nasulitan nay pabalucu'ay a kawaw nu subana'ay a pu 2018-1, nasulitan ni Tuku Sayun.

kasolin micaliw to lebong adada' ko tangila sapoelac ngato cacay ano mikacaw kami to kasolin , kya kasolin macaliw to lebong saca bohang sa, caay haw kiso adada' ko tangila ? kanahanto matengil to ko soni',caay to kapah ko soni', caay kasiwatan ko soni' haw? kya mahiza saw? oyniyan sa, o tangila no mita, ilabo' a tangila, sipiatep nay bali kya. izaw ko dohpicay a telis , kya ngangan no holam sa, o "komoo鼓膜". ilabo' no komoo maziket tolo a wokak, taneng patodo' ninel no komoo, tina kakitizaan singangan ko "teban-tangila ". i demiad sa, o bali-sapiatep no teban-tangila mahiza no hekalay, taneng sapalalen . nika ano ihekalay a bali-sapiatep tasol talakaw saca poenel sa, oyniyan a sapiatep caay to sapalalen, bocici to ko talakaway a bali-sapiatep tayza poenelay-sapiatep. ko komoo talabo' saca tahekal, caay to kakapah ko tangila no mita. ngatoc tosa micomod to lebong ko kasolin, kya bali-sapiatep tansol amatasasa', talakaw to ko bali-sapiatep ilabo' no teban-tangila, ozama sa, bocici to ko komoo nay labo' tahekal. sisa, adada' to ko tangila no mita. mahiza to mikacaw to hikoki, tapabaw ko hikoki, adada' to ko tangila no mita. osakasa, mapoenel ko bali-sapiatep ihekal no hikoki. o belih sa, ano mikacaw kami to tianti , tansol sa tasasa' kya tianti, tansol talakaw ko bali-sapiatep no tianti. bocici komoo nay hekal talabo', mahiza sa, adada' to ko tangila no mita. mosepi , sihoso matolin teban-tangil ato cihe-salaedan(鼻腔,salaedan空間), o tangila-takolaw-hoso . pisowab saca pienoc taneng mibohat to tangila-takolaw-hoso, miedap sapalaen bali-sapiatep no teban-tangil aot hekal-tangila . ano mahiza sa, caay to kaadada' ko tangila. namakayniyan a nasolitan nasakamowan ato natinengan Wikipayke paybaloco'ay polongamin a codad-耳 Protein behind hearing 3D Ear page Details of varioos ear problems Ear wiggling mechanism onmasked Cotton swabs can pose serioos health risk: coroner from ctv.ca nasolitan nay pabaloco'ay a kawaw no sobana'ay a po 2018-1, nasolitan ni Toko Sayon.
